{"tid":585480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出車捱撞癱瘓交通  九巴工聯會工會副主任黎兆聰頸痛入院","createTime":"2018-03-08T16:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T02:46:49.000Z","uid":23861,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8138ffea4c00994fbe7aa1db3b4186be4c3b9a7e","tid":585480,"uid":23861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T16:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180308/s00001/3f3a0c5f992d9ffaed631a967632013c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180308%2Fs00001%2F3f3a0c5f992d9ffaed631a967632013c.jpg&h=39432e55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180308/s00001/3f3cccf9e498f2b7552b9fa9b3c7a5a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180308%2Fs00001%2F3f3cccf9e498f2b7552b9fa9b3c7a5a4.jpg&h=1f5a2d43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傍晚近7時，九巴一輛3M線雙層巴士沿清水灣道二線往彩雲方向行駛，其間一輛的士由一線切至二線時與之碰撞。45歲巴士車長受傷送院，附近交通一度嚴重擠塞。據悉傷者是汽車交通運輸業總工會九巴分會副主任黎兆聰，報稱頸痛由救護車送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n上月10日大埔九巴意外造成19人死亡，黎兆聰曾指出車長須承受很大壓力，有時又要面對乘客指罵，希望大家包容。<span style=\"color: red;\">早前九巴「月薪車長大聯盟」發起人葉蔚琳發起罷工，黎曾不點名批評：「我哋（汽總）係好理性嘅工會，唔學啲白癡，搞按章工作、一人罷工。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180227/large/1519727279_62b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180227%2Flarge%2F1519727279_62b2.jpg&h=3fca112d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180308/s00001/1520524668128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180308%2Fs00001%2F1520524668128&d=8jSl%2F07Erb5WLRU5GsSSW9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=b87d0764\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180308%2Fs00001%2F1520524668128&h=a8bc53eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180308/s00001/1520524668128</a>"},{"pid":"8d8dd62a167a5905785b4bfe0318e413ba79b834","tid":585480,"uid":171107,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T16:46:26.000Z","msg":"咁快有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254a8f0deb2ff7dc00498f2b0f8eba27d1cfd289","tid":585480,"uid":21139,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T16:50:05.000Z","msg":"咁都撞唔死佢，天冇眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d69993401b6aff0c18d8c1599c93d7d98408d54a","tid":585480,"uid":23861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T16:57:01.000Z","msg":"另類既擺工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaeb74e419ea89c721c1eac036e5f8e5e97a81c0","tid":585480,"uid":96658,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T17:00:58.000Z","msg":"好高端<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔按章工作係咁既意思<br />\n天才嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbbb278a63a67da294171d2f981854cc50483fd0","tid":585480,"uid":4783,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T17:22:09.000Z","msg":"原來唔罷工係咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n撞車之後報頸痛就唔洗開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7f3570bc601df3e0df3916c802fb4dd97cb4cb","tid":585480,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-